90&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=815cc92dda88379a6cf8ef3ab1390543" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3369867020052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=229&amp;h=290&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=815cc92dda88379a6cf8ef3ab1390543" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1"></figcaption><div class="scrapImageButtonWrapper_sqv0cmd"><k-scrap-image-button data-image-id="DSXZQO3369867020052023000000" data-scrapping="true" data-image-url="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3369867020052023000000-1.jpg?s=d80ad462fa366e5fc24b038fe60f1e3d" data-image-alt="" class="container_c1d2uus7"><button class="button_bmoqgjl icon_ignni8g default_d1abwhe7 default_d1nd2e1a" disabled="" data-scrap-image-button="true" data-popover-target="scrap-image-button"></button></k-scrap-image-button></div></div></div></figure><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">最近的涨幅来自主要的制造业股。与 2011 年 2 月底的收盘价相比，西门子上涨了 10%，超过了 DAX 6% 的涨幅。这是因为一直以来对盈利造成压力的能源价格飙升已经得到解决。据Refinitiv称，欧洲天然气指数荷兰TTF次月交货价18日时隔约1年零11个月首次跌破30欧元/MWh。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb"> “德国也可能从中国的经济重新开放中受益，”英国巴克莱银行的 Emmanuel Cau 说。占其2022年大中华区销售额10%以上的阿迪达斯股价上涨12%。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">不过，鉴于欧洲央行(ECB)预计将继续加息以应对极高的通胀，德股是否会进一步上涨尚不明朗。</p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 19 May 2023 20:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOGR19EAN0Z10C23A5000000/</guid><link/> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOGR19EAN0Z10C23A5000000/<category>全球市场</category><category>国外</category><category>库存</category><category>欧洲</category></item></channel></rss>